      <title>中国告诉伊朗，以色列遇袭后合作将持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-tells-iran-cooperation-will-last-after-attack-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高外交官告诉伊朗，两国未来可以在一系列领域开展合作，这表明在德黑兰对以色列发动前所未有的袭击后，两国关系仍然牢固。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-tells-iran-cooperation-will-last-after-attack-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 02:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普依靠一小群富有的捐助者来资助竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/election-2024-campaign-finance-trump-relies-on-small-group-of-rich-donors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦选举委员会最新披露的信息显示，唐纳德·特朗普依靠一小群富有的捐助者捐赠了 2360 万美元，约占他和共和党 3 月份筹集资金的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/election-2024-campaign-finance-trump-relies-on-small-group-of-rich-donors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 02:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹恩惠“谦虚地”接受选举失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/south-korean-president-yoon-humbly-accepts-election-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在其保守党上周在议会选举中惨败后首次公开发表讲话，承诺将更密切地倾听人民的声音，改善贫困人口的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/south-korean-president-yoon-humbly-accepts-election-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡李显龙为下一任总理黄之锋铺平道路，观察家们怎么说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/singapore-s-lee-paves-way-for-wong-after-20-years-as-pm-voices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理李显龙将于 5 月 15 日卸任，任职二十年后。 72 岁的李将把权力移交给 51 岁的副手劳伦斯·黄 (Lawrence Wong)，这一交接被广泛报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/singapore-s-lee-paves-way-for-wong-after-20-years-as-pm-voices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使前往朝鲜边境继续向平壤施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-envoy-heads-to-korean-border-to-keep-pressure-on-pyongyang</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻联合国大使前往朝韩两国分隔的非军事区，加大对朝鲜的压力，制裁执行受到沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-envoy-heads-to-korean-border-to-keep-pressure-on-pyongyang</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
